    %p
      Powered by
      %em.icon-cogs
        %a{:href => "https://github.com/eunomie/wlt", :target => "_blank"}
          Web Log Today
    %p
      Généré le
      = DateTime.now.strftime "%F"
      à partir des
      %a{:href => "https://github.com/CrEv/log.winsos.net", :target => "_blank"}
        sources
